{"tid":807991,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 素顏蔡少芬白滑美肌唔似44歲","createTime":"2018-09-06T03:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T08:49:39.000Z","uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84be42547afe22d7db672c6cfd4b83d90b7f7ef0","tid":807991,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"藝人蔡少芬（Ada）同老公張晉結婚十年，生咗兩個可愛嘅囡囡，但依然恩愛如昔，真係令人羨慕！ <br />\n<br />\n呢日兩公婆仲喺社交網打情罵俏晒恩愛，話說Ada上載兩張素顏相，對鏡頭笑得燦爛嘅佢留言讚老公：「出自你手，實是佳作！」跟住張晉即刻轉載呢兩張相，再留言回覆老婆：「模特美，模特美[可愛]」網民見到都覺得眼冤，忍唔住留言話：「知道了，知道了，全世界都知道你老婆最美！！！」不過相中嘅Ada雖然冇化妝，但近鏡下皮膚白滑緊緻，完全唔似就快踏入45歲，幸福嘅婚姻果然係女人最佳嘅化妝品！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/114324_6f787285378276ac18921e8d7940321f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F114324_6f787285378276ac18921e8d7940321f.png&h=39809bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">1991年蔡少芬還未滿18歲便當選港姐季軍；同年，她在麗晶酒店（洲際酒店前身）舉行百萬生日會慶祝生日，有傳是香港富商劉鑾雄付款，另外劉鑾雄亦傳付出逾億元代蔡少芬母還賭債。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/06/114349_09c2311bc35c452f46f0f5c24b21b225.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F114349_09c2311bc35c452f46f0f5c24b21b225.png&h=ee69a373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">劉鑾雄的前妻，寶詠琴最喜歡蔡少芬，還特地請老師幫她補習英語，教她社交禮儀，以便陪劉鑾雄出席各種場合。</span>"},{"pid":"bf9f16e339184be0badc448b9a7ad72e44fe19fc","tid":807991,"uid":36296,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"留名睇蔡少芬&gt;韓妹圖"},{"pid":"9ac0d10554101e101503353633f2d862f9c63a32","tid":807991,"uid":94501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"對邊個好呀而家我呀？"},{"pid":"11e698e3a747b9172c5c4d3b058e6bfbfea0eae8","tid":807991,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"對ada仲好！！！！"},{"pid":"f511ce79e737821147db98e3f52fb023a3c45e65","tid":807991,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:54:47.000Z","msg":"人乾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333a86763dad067d08ca26823ab3d2681196ea45","tid":807991,"uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"成街人都睇死你開公司，仲開戲畀佢拍呀！咁多聯絡架？唔洗講野啦我地。"},{"pid":"22c53b1d15cf7339a0a445b57c3dcf4694f81098","tid":807991,"uid":69168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"個眼皮塌哂都話唔似44....."},{"pid":"87f8d89c5981d7c206307cb3751f474b96138006","tid":807991,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"佢把拆喉聲出賣咗佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人把聲咁 個樣幾後生都頂唔順"},{"pid":"d4c8e2547069d4a57f64a2395f8e336947983a76","tid":807991,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120206/large/06ec1p12new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120206%2Flarge%2F06ec1p12new.jpg&h=371e87d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2661c920837f52765d98c6783cf343bf0c7e90c","tid":807991,"uid":14065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"你對皮膚唔好咩"},{"pid":"6d483ea345e714afeba381e9547c0a0ae2241860","tid":807991,"uid":91317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"似54"},{"pid":"128f84efe217ab5cb31627cf0cbcc881ca534df8","tid":807991,"uid":50399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2661c920837f52765d98c6783cf343bf0c7e90c","tid":807991,"uid":14065,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"你對皮